# Claude Code rewrites ~/.claude/settings.json at runtime: it reshuffles key
# order and persists runtime prefs like effortLevel (set by /effort). Both
# would otherwise churn this repo (the file is symlinked in). The
# `claude-settings` clean filter sorts keys and drops effortLevel so those
# don't diff; other real value changes still diff. Filter in mac/gitconfig.
claude-settings.json filter=claude-settings
